<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Wikiful</title>
	<!--[if lt IE 9]> <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js" type="text/javascript"></script> <![endif]-->
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", media: "all", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
 <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport">
</head>
<body>

<div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
  <div class="navbar-inner">
    <div class="container">
      <%= link_to "Wikiful", root_path, :class => "brand" %>
       <div class="session-controls"> 
          <% if current_user %>
            <%= link_to "Log Out", logout_path, :class => 'btn btn-primary btn-mini' %>
            Logged in as <%= current_user.email %>.
          <% else %>
            <div class="btn-group">
              <%= link_to "Sign Up", signup_path, :class => "btn btn-mini" %>
              <%= link_to "Log In", login_path, :class => "btn btn-mini" %>
            </div>
          <% end %>
       </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span9"><%= yield %></div>

	<div class="span3 sidebar">
	  <div class="my-wiki-site">
	    <h4>My Wikiful</h4>
	    <ul>
	      <li><%= link_to "Write a Wiki", new_article_path %></li>
	    </ul>
	  </div>

	<div class="row">
	  <div class="span4">
	    <% flash.each do |name, msg| %>
	      <%= content_tag :div, msg, id: "flash_#{name}" %>
	    <% end %>
	  </div>
	</div>

	  <div class="categories-sidebar">
	    <h4>Categories</h4>
	    <ul>
	      <% @categories.each do |category| %>
		<li><%= link_to category.name, category %></li>
	      <% end %>
	    </ul>
	  </div>
	  <div class="about">
	    <h4>About Wikiful</h4>
	    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Accusantium architecto earum neque perspiciatis quia animi debitis quod repellat vitae explicabo. Sapiente aliquam reprehenderit id vitae atque ducimus facere molestias soluta?</p>
	  </div>
	</div>

  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
